Ingredients (12)
1 cup plain yoghurt (thick)
1 garlic clove, crushed
2cm piece ginger, peeled, grated
1 tbsp lemon juice
1 tbsp olive oil
1 tsp garam masala
1 tsp ground coriander
1/2 tsp chilli powder
1/2 tsp turmeric
6 chicken thigh fillets, trimmed
Brown rice, cooked, to serve
Lemon wedges, to serve
